{"tid":175844,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］如果要教人廣東話","createTime":"2017-03-27T18:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T11:28:15.000Z","uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6332004e09567b988a7dcd95e73d3e0c6769849c","tid":175844,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"點先最好？<br />\n有冇人記得細個點學廣東話？<br />\n啲讀音用拼音？<br />\n網上有冇咩完整好用教材？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887f6f00c2023882708c483d93c45f56879b82cd","tid":175844,"uid":90247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:26:16.000Z","msg":"粗口學起"},{"pid":"4939fe4a87134cf48b7283cf059fc9eacc685464","tid":175844,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T23:02:50.000Z","msg":"細個無人會學拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b71c9335ee7e52e2b6dc64c868c68bcdd2c279b","tid":175844,"uid":50320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T23:09:27.000Z","msg":"睇下佢有幾多時間，由動詞學起, 逐個字配詞造句,慢慢學is ok.。教左拼音會有幫助，對自學同自己温習特別有幫助。如果要認埋字就要整埋教材，因為認字先係non chinese speaker既死穴。<br />\n<br />\n利申：ncs小學中文老師"},{"pid":"b4570cf1e2ff6ae78d2ff25fd56c86f24282d5cb","tid":175844,"uid":34032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T23:19:28.000Z","msg":"同問 想知點樣學廣東話拼音？係咪都係上網搵resources, 定係出面會有班教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63cebf9ed73cd92b69c89706e6d1b9a55ca2292","tid":175844,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T23:22:31.000Z","msg":"細個 廣東話就係母語<br />\n教人講點同你由母語學起<br />\n因為學嗰個人嘅母語已經係第2種"},{"pid":"5049351c458fc4a549b2922b491a1ad00688d853","tid":175844,"uid":50320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T23:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問 想知點樣學廣東話拼音？係咪都係上網搵resources, 定係出面會有班教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得拼音自學好難，一定要上堂先學得好。金 細拆開黎 就係 家(g) 奄(am) 1聲 所以係gam1 不過就算係廣東話拼音都有幾種方法 對外國人黎講 可能用羅馬化個隻拼音會容易好多，例如個金字 maybe  gum1  is better than gam1 to the foreigners"},{"pid":"2f24972816ffc063fde39ffba9599c7879f21734","tid":175844,"uid":50320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T23:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問 想知點樣學廣東話拼音？係咪都係上網搵resources, 定係出面會有班教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果巴打有興趣既可以免費交流下 我都係半桶水其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難得仲有人想學廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3063044c445bb1e641463a6e97a0e7cd1888c05a","tid":175844,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"教粗口易記d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf399ff51afd0747b8970b350257d5aec66452d","tid":175844,"uid":29247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"要睇佢係大人定小朋友<br />\n大人一般會教拼音先（耶魯式），小朋友我就唔會教拼音，叫佢地用自己方法記得就算<br />\n聽講方面由日常對話入手<br />\n再分類學生字<br />\n例如數字，食物，運動之類<br />\n<br />\n閱讀方面要睇佢學既目的係咩<br />\n如果只係為日常生活我會畀粵文佢地睇<br />\n如果係小朋友為升學就要學埋書面語"},{"pid":"27425e83fbe3c3308534452f4bdfc76fa5164655","tid":175844,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個無人會學拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講緊教人啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a84a1c809751fbcee068f0a65b0201f40704a07","tid":175844,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>粗口學起</blockquote><br />\n呢層就梗咖喇"},{"pid":"7b4f9f87a7f06515491e4d4188c72241bd6f0c67","tid":175844,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同問 想知點樣學廣東話拼音？係咪都係上網搵resources, 定係出面會有班教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得拼音自學好難，一定要上堂先學得好。金 細拆開黎 就係 家(g) 奄(am) 1聲 所以係gam1 不過就算係廣東話拼音都有幾種方法 對外國人黎講 可能用羅馬化個隻拼音會容易好多，例如個金字 maybe  gum1  is better than gam1 to the foreigners</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我要教嘅人本身已經識中文<br />\n所以應該易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係拼音我真係唔知點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身為香港人嘅自己我都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咩教材可以買/上網有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e850d92822ace0bed6e164372b6dfc4f3ec5a865","tid":175844,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:07:41.000Z","msg":"法國廣東話好似真係一份正正經經嘅教材都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7f9393099ee617ad3f21a0ae5a60746cdc2830","tid":175844,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7db01d2d84377db1ff7056e0130edc93e2452c1","tid":175844,"uid":50320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:28:15.000Z","msg":"教材網上有好多 前提係你有冇呢d語言學知識 如果冇既話 有教材都冇用 廣東話拼音 都係學聲 韻 調 3 樣野姐 上網揾番個字表 對住黎讀就ok啦"}]}